
The following is temporary hackery I used to get things started.

Planning proper build approach at some point this year.

 - --
 - git clone libhybris on device
    - see https://github.com/libhybris/libhybris/wiki/Building
 - install Android headers Pie 9 API level 28
    - see https://github.com/ubports/android-headers.git
 - patch libhybris
    - see ../patches/hybris-diffs
 - build libhybris locally, install
    - see ./ut-debs.txt
 - replace o.so
    - see ./hybris-opt-tree
 - --
 - setprop service.sf.present_timestamp banana
    - any fruit works here
 - export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/libhybris/lib:/vendor/lib:/system/lib
 - export HYBRIS_VULKANPLATFORM=null
    - see ./bashrc
 - --




